Package jalse.tags

This package provides the Tag functionality.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Tag
    Tags are used to provide internal state information without polluting the data model.
    Taggable
    Used identify any class that is exposing internal state through Tag.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntityType
    A Tag used to help identify an Entity marked by type.
    Parent
    An immutable Tag used to identify a direct parent.
    TagTypeSet
    A tag set is a thread-safe Set implementation for Tag.

Package jalse.tags Description

This package provides the Tag functionality. Tags are read-only states that can change during runtime.
See Also:
TagTypeSet, EntityType, Parent
